name: The Holy Ghost Is Moving
chorusText:
The Holy Ghost is moving
The Holy Ghost is moving through this land
Reach out and touch Him while you can
from the high, high mountain
to the low, low valley
The Holy Ghost is moving through this land.
Refrain
Praise the Lord                      x2
Let all God’s people praise the Lord
Shake off those heavy burdens
Lift up those holy hands
Let all God’s people praise the Lord
